{"tid":664046,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[仲有無人記得媽媽Mia] 嫁內地富二代　「模媽」陳靜儀閃婚想再生","createTime":"2018-05-13T19:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T07:16:58.000Z","uid":49391,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d201b2249efdd4531ea166fb7758824eca0ced51","tid":664046,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T19:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180513/photo/bkn-20180513230904580-0513_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180514001641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180513%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180513230904580-0513_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180514001641&h=d4b2c058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「模媽」陳靜儀近年淡出娛樂圈，有讀者爆料指她改名為「陳樂庭（Flora）」兼和拍拖數月的內地富二代、身家十億的男友Martin結婚！東網發現她於上周五在尖沙咀半島酒店舉行西式婚宴，布置浪漫奢華，更有以男友及其新洋名字首「MF」的設計字樣。據有份出席的賓客透露，陳靜儀未有邀請圈中人，又指她曾表示想早日為丈夫開枝散葉，並會在北京及香港兩邊走，而陳靜儀未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180513/photo/bkn-20180513230904580-0513_00862_001_02b.jpg?20180514001641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180513%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180513230904580-0513_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20180514001641&h=60483cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳靜儀與身家十億的男友Martin在半島擺酒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180513/bkn-20180513230904580-0513_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180513%2Fbkn-20180513230904580-0513_00862_001.html&d=fezImUaJIW98Y1M5V9kxHU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=b85e43ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180513/bkn-20180513230904580-0513_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n改埋名洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944c7fd2d2e3482aedb32d194725273960398b47","tid":664046,"uid":73225,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T19:12:10.000